<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Sorte Sua</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
  <meta http-equiv="content-language" content="pt-br">
  <meta name="author" content="Luiz Augusto">
  <meta name="keywords" content="loteria, caixa, lotofacil, conferir, resultados, automaticamente, automatico, mega-sena, quina">
  <meta name="description" content="Confira seus resultados nas loterias brasileiras automaticamente.">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <![endif]-->
  <script type="text/javascript">

    var _gaq = _gaq || [];
    _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-10878888-3']);
    _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);

    (function() {
      var ga = document.createElement('script'); ga.type = 'text/javascript'; ga.async = true;
      ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' : 'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';
      var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);
    })();

  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </a>

        <%= link_to 'Sorte Sua', root_path, :class => 'brand' %>

        <div class="nav-collapse">
          <ul class="nav">
            <li class="divider-vertical"></li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Login', new_user_session_path %></li>
            <li class="divider-vertical"></li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Cadastrar', new_user_registration_path %></li>
            <li class="divider-vertical"></li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Contato', '#' %></li>
            <li class="divider-vertical"></li>        
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span8 offset2">
        <%= content_tag(:p, notice, :class => 'notice alert alert-success') if notice.present? %>
        <%= content_tag(:p, alert, :class => 'alert') if alert.present? %>
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-unit">
      <h1>Sorte Sua</h1>
      <p>
        Confira automaticamente os seus resultados nas loterias brasileiras! Basta se cadastrar e inserir suas apostas para ver quantos pontos vocês fez no concurso atual e nos próximos. <br /> <br />
        <%= link_to 'Faça login', new_user_session_path, :class => 'btn btn-large'%> ou <%= link_to 'Cadastre-se', new_user_registration_path, :class => 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-header">
      <span class="round-img">
        <img src="/assets/header.png" class="img"/>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
